{"tid":1788720,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"中国旅行團去年加拿大車禍　死傷者家屬索賠近30億港元","createTime":"2019-12-19T01:54:19.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-19T03:18:35.000Z","uid":184679,"like":5,"dislike":10,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"d16b1c1ce2808a19c5c57aed682d938f39d07e47","tid":1788720,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-19T01:54:19.000Z","msg":"一個中國旅行團去年在加拿大遇到車禍，造成3人死亡，超過20人受傷，死傷者家屬入稟當地法院，要求賠償5億加幣，相當於近30億港元。<br />\n<br />\n根據相關法庭文件，被控的美籍華裔司機在意外發生時，除了超速駕駛，更用手機發短訊，之後旅遊巴失事，撞到路邊岩石翻側。死傷者的家屬向這名司機、旅遊巴公司及交通部門提出索償，指司機未能做好駕駛工作，旅遊巴公司亦未能正確培訓司機、未確實檢查車輛。涉事司機早前已經被起訴。 <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1497905-20191216.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1497905-20191216.htm&d=CSzjam5d59%2B0TSQi2Kgm6o6aL69TDc1SPHZju%2B%2BXLiQ%3D&h=e2ac3231\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1497905-20191216.htm&h=4e68db3d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1497905-20191216.htm</a>"},{"pid":"efd30c3c47aecfc27ba86264ff1456dee4ae61c6","tid":1788720,"uid":289733,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-19T02:02:27.000Z","msg":"啲大劣人係外國就大大聲阿支阿佐，屌人唔駛本，返到大陸，佢地夠胆出聲？做返死狗啦。<br />\n馬航單野，有人出黎告嗎？告條鐵啦&hellip; 門口狗"},{"pid":"f3a11df25d1e7353158ffd9027a5b22643903d56","tid":1788720,"uid":39846,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-19T02:08:38.000Z","msg":"挑你咪叫大啲個價囉，睇你返支那先被打税，再被逃税，之後收歸國有<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"67fcf05bfa2bdc9d239b7625e6a23a8e4e508860","tid":1788720,"uid":165749,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-19T02:13:47.000Z","msg":"啲錢俾哂黑警出OT啦，你要既就問黑警羅"},{"pid":"8587469cf8f0cc44af6b29cb38b990d04e312c58","tid":1788720,"uid":14494,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-19T02:24:28.000Z","msg":"比卡超：去得加拿大就要承擔風險"},{"pid":"018bec